      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>The creature can attempt to summon creatures of the same creature type as itself as a full action. The summoned ally returns to the place from which it came after 1 hour.</p>\n<p><em>Format</em>:<strong>Spell-Like Abilities</strong> 1/day—summon allies (1 imp 60%).</p>\n<p><em>Guidelines</em>: Choose either a creature of the same CR as the monster (with a 35% chance of success) or a creature with a CR no greater than the monster’s CR – 5 (with a 60% chance of success).</p>"
